Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(西伦敦最佳)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.49,0:00:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 伙计们 抱歉我迟到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Morning, fellas. Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要理一下思绪 所以我决定走路来上班\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just needed to clear my head so I decided to, you know, walk to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果我发现在一个不太了解的城市 边走边理思绪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Turns out that clearing and walking in a town you don't know all too well
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难度有点大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}can be a little tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.71,0:00:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后我迷路了 但是之后 我又迷路了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ended up getting lost but, you know, then I got unlost,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三次迷路了 但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}then I got lost again but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是到这儿了 彼尔德在 内特也在 这很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, you know, now I'm here, you know. Beard's here, Nate's here, which is great
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这世界可能是一个 悲伤孤独的地方 但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because the world can be a sad, lonely place, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 不说那些了 开始工作吧?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, come on now, let's get to work, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.68,0:00:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Michelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Which is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 因为我正好可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, it's okay, 'cause it's a great time now for me to,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把自己埋在工作里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you know, bury myself in my work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.94,0:01:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以...不过 我没疯...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And so-- Although, I'm not crazy--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢“埋”这个词 明白我的意思吧?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't love the word "bury," you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听上去就不是很吉利 对吧?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just got a negative connotation to it, don't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能换成哪个词呢?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's another word I could say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都喜欢泡澡 对吗? 舒服的热水澡 是吧?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everyone loves a good bath, right? Just a nice warm bath, right? Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就用这个词好了 我要说 “我要把自己泡在工作里”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So that's what I'll say. I'll say, "I'm gonna bathe myself in work."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.78,0:01:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?听上去好多了 很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How 'bout that? That's good. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,内特 你有喜欢的气泡弹吗 伙计?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nate, you got a favorite bath bomb, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 我不是很喜欢泡澡 因为皮肤会泡得皱皱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I just don't really enjoy baths, just 'cause my skin gets really wrinkly,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我非常担忧变老这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I'm deeply worried about aging.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.17,0:01:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我理解 你呢 教练? 你有没有喜欢的气泡弹?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, I get that. What about you, Coach? You got a favorite bath bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,焦糖奶油蜂蜜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Crème brûlée honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.34,0:01:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蜂蜜?这是一种成分 还是你觉得我和蜜一样甜?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Honey? Is that an ingredient or something you just called me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-成分 -该死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Ingredient. -Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是后者呢 但这个主意挺有趣的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was hoping it was the other one. But that's kind of a fun idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们可以用昵称来称呼彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe we start calling each other little pet names.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如说“亲爱的”或是“宝贝”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know? Like "honey" or "babe," you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺不错的吧?你觉得呢 教练?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It might be nice, right? What do you think, Coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,内特 能帮我个忙吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nate, will you do me a favor here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能帮教练计划一下今天的训练吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Will you just help Coach plan practice for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好的 没问题 -很好 谢谢 亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Absolutely. Yeah. -All right. Thank you, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 一会见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, I'll see y'all in a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他没事吧? -有事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Is he all right? -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(♪我们是里士满)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 开始吧 萨拉 你来开个头吧?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right. Shall we? Sarah, why don't you lead us off?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉索教练 你终于赢了你的第一场比赛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, Coach Lasso. You finally won your first match.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉如何?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How's it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉 我相信有时即使比分赢过对手 但依然是输家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, Sarah, I believe you can outscore your opponent and still lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如即使你比分比对手更少 你也依然是赢家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just like you can score less than them and win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但上周我们确实赢了 非常令人开心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But last week we definitely won, which is pretty darn fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 下一个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《独立报》的特伦特克里姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Trent Crimm, <i>The Independent</i>.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是否可以猜测杰米塔特 下一场比赛会回到球场?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is it safe to assume that Jamie Tartt will be back on the pitch next match?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道人们对猜测这件事 怎么说的吗 特伦特?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, you know what they say when you assume, Trent?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把咱俩都变成了傻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You make an arse outta you and me. Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是另一个经典案例\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And that right there is another example
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:03:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的英语和你们的英语 有时候并不兼容 对吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of how our English and y'all's English sometimes do not jive, innit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你真的打算让最好的球员坐冷板凳吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But are you honestly gonna keep your best player on the bench?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这取决于杰米 他知道我们需要他做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, that depends on Jamie. He knows what we need from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一个问题 奇普 问吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's keep it going, yeah? Kip, come on, hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-泰德 我正好要找你 -嘿 老板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Ted. Just the man I wanted to see. -Hey, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你让杰米塔特坐冷板凳的决定 真的非常勇敢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your decision to bench Jamie Tartt was very brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢 -这是一招妙棋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Thank you. -I mean, a masterstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想这种说法已经过时了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think we're allowed to talk like that at work anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一件事比较棘手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's just one complication now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曼城打电话来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Manchester City have called,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们想问能不能终止杰米的租借\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and they've inquired about terminating Jamie's loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他们要收走他的房子? -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-They're gonna take his house? -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰德 杰米的合同是和曼城签的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ted, Jamie's contract is owned by Manchester City,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们这个赛季把他借给了里士满\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and they, in turn, loaned him to Richmond for the season.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我懂了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你让他坐冷板凳 他们计划收回他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They want Jamie back if you are planning to bench him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这么计划的 我计划让我的计划成功\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not planning on that. No, my plan is for my plan to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但俗话说得好 人算不如天算 对吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you know what they say about the best-laid plans, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说太多遍“计划”了 我快不认识这个词了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Said "plan" too many times. Word's lost all its meaning now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,计划 计划 计划 无所谓了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Plan. Plan. Plan. Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟曼城说 这个人另有计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, you tell Man City that this man has a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-计划 计划 计划? -计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Plan. Plan. Plan? -Plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:03:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-计划? -嘴不要咧开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Plan? -Not plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-计划 -类似“果酱馅饼”的发音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Plan. -Like "flan." Plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果酱馅饼?那道甜品吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Flan? That dessert?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 果酱馅饼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, like "flan."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不太喜欢吃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I don't dig on flan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,计划 计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Plan. Plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,计划 计划?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Plan. Plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-只用声音交流了? -那叫什么来着?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Word become a sound? -What's that called again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-语义饱和 -对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Semantic satiation. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个新来的墨西哥孩子还没到?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is that new kid from Mexico here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他在治疗他的膝盖 -好吧 很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-He's getting treatment on his knee. -Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他叫什么来着? -丹尼罗哈斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-What's his name again? -Dani Rojas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这名字不错 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. It's a great name. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰米怎么样了?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How's Jamie doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说他受伤了 今天不能参加训练\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Says he can't practice today. Says he's hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要出事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 杰米\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, Jamie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说你今天不能跟我们一起训练 是这样吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I heard you're not gonna be able to run with us today. That true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我受伤了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Cause I'm hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾听到这个消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Really sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放松 泰德 只是训练而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Relax, Ted. It's just practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说你不能训练 没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you can't practice, you can't practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说你受伤了 没问题 就这么简单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you're hurt, you're hurt. It's as simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这些都不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But it ain't about that... at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你坐在这里 你应该是球队的支柱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're sitting in here. You're supposed to be the franchise player.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可我们却在讨论你缺席的训练\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And yet here we are, talking about you missing practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们谈的是训练\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're talking about practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗?训练\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You understand me? Practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是比赛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是你去拼尽全力的比赛 对吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not a game. Not the game you go out there and die for. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,周末也踢 仿佛是你最后一场比赛 对吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Play every weekend like it's your last, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们谈的是训练 兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, we're talking about practice, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,训练!你知道你应该参加的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Practice! You know you're supposed to be out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你应该树立榜样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know you're supposed to lead by example.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把这些都抛在脑后了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're just shoving that all aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 杰米 我们现在谈论的是训练\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And so here we are, Jamie. We're talking about practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是比赛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是比赛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们谈的是训练 和球队一起 和你的队友一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're talking about practice, with your team. With your teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一一个我们可以一起踢球的地方 我们可以掌控的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The only place we get to play together, we got control over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其余时间是我们11人 对阵对手的11人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Rest of the time it's us 11 against those 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们谈的是训练 兄弟!\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're talking about practice, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我谈的是训练! 你参加不了 因为你受伤了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm talking about practice! And you can't do it 'cause you're hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没意见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你讲 帮我个忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell you what. Do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你出去的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When you get out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把锥形道具放好 这样其他人还能做一些传球练习\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}set up the cones so the other reserves can do a little passing drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你让我放道具? -非常感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-You want me to set up cones? -I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-科林 你去弄 -他点名要你去的 伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Colin, go set the cones up. -I think he asked you, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在跟你说话吗 大块头?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Was I talking to you, big man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科林 快去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Colin, set up the cones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾萨克说得对 教练让你去 你是替补队员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Isaac's right. He asked you. You are a second-teamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太伤自尊了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's gotta sting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须得说 看到杰米被挫了锐气 我还挺开心的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I must say, it's quite nice seeing Jamie put in his place for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-甚至有些激动 对吗? -不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Thrilling even, innit? -No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要幸灾乐祸 好吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is a no schadenfreude zone, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不准幸灾乐祸 -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-<i>Nein schadenfreude.</i> -All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新来的那孩子 他叫...丹尼什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The new kid, what's his-- Dani what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-罗哈斯 -罗哈斯 他踢得怎么样?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Rojas. -Rojas, yeah. Is he any good?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏季球员转会期过来的 随后就受伤了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Came here in the summer transfer window, was immediately injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-所以没人看过他踢球 -没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-so no one's really seen him play. -That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为一旦杰米看到有人顶替了他的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, 'cause once Jamie sees someone else playing his position,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道...他会很不爽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you know... I mean, it's gonna hurt his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 我不应该这么开心的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm so sorry. I shouldn't be happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我们要让但你尽快适应 好吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, let's be sure to help Dani get acclimated, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次加入这个球队肯定会不知所措\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}First time in this league can be very overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼罗哈斯 罗哈斯!丹尼罗哈斯!\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dani Rojas, Rojas! Dani Rojas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗哈斯 丹尼罗哈斯!罗哈斯!\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Rojas, Dani Rojas! Rojas, Rojas, Rojas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿!你们好 教练们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey! Hello, coaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-感谢你们给我这个机会 -你是一个很有活力的年轻人 丹尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Thank you for the opportunity. -Yeah. You are a spirited fella, Dani.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去场上踢前锋看看 好吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just go on out there, and get the striker spot for us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好极了!跟瓜达拉哈拉那时那样 你怎么说我就怎么做 教练\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes! Just like back in Guadalajara, you say it, I do it, Coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,足球就是生命!\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Football is life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰米不喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jamie doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种笨蛋一上场准露馅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Chipper dickheads like that can never back it up on the pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的传球 山姆!\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Beautiful cross, Sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,足球就是生命!\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Football is life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也说不准 感觉他蛮厉害的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't really tell, but it seems like he's very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cheers, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一些待业的教练问我们近期有没有空缺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And some unemployed gaffers are asking if we'll have an opening soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托尼普利斯 阿兰科比什利 哈瑞雷德內普打过三次电话了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tony Pulis. Alan Curbishley. Harry Redknapp called three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 我昨晚一夜没睡 仔细研究了所有球员的背景\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi. I've been up all night doing deep dives on all the players.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道理查德是在一个牧羊场长大的吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you know that Richard was raised on a goat farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有 艾萨克的妈妈有两只左手?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And that Isaac's mother has two left hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还联系了几个熟人 了解了一下赞助机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I called a couple of contacts about some sponsorship opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至还给自己弄了一个日程本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Even got myself a little work planner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能买个没有“独角兽”的吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You couldn't get one without the word "unicorn" written on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滚开啦 独角兽多可爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fuck off. It's adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我忍不住会想如果我让你滚 你会有什么反应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sorry, I couldn't help but think how you'd react if I told you to F off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没事了 你出去吧 希金斯 -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-That'll be all, Higgins. -Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到你笑我真的很开心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm really glad to see that you're laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是来看看你是否一切安好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just came by to see if you're okay, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会不好?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why wouldn't I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天 你还没看新闻吧?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, Christ. Have you not seen the news yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来是想来安慰你的 而不是把坏消息带给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I really wanted to be the one to comfort you, not to break it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得那个漂亮女孩 叫贝克丝?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, you remember that stunning girl, Bex?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庆典当日和鲁伯特一起离开的那位?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The one that Rupert left with the night of the gala?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我假装她不是绝世大美女?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you really want me to pretend that she wasn't mad fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我要谢谢你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那个丑八怪 她叫贝克丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, well. That hideous cow, whose name's Bex,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-其实是个简称 她其实叫... -瑞贝卡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-which is actually short for... -Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 刚好你们同名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yep, which is also your name, as you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以媒体称她为...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So the press is calling her--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“新瑞贝卡” 该死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"New Rebecca." Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媒体称她为“瑞贝卡” 而你是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The press is calling her "Rebecca," and you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“老瑞贝卡”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Old Rebecca."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什么? -老瑞贝卡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-What? -Old Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老瑞贝卡?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Old Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 你可以的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't worry about it. You've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你撑不住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And if you ever have a moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是你应付不来了 你可以打给我 好吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or if you don't got this, then you just call me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇!你是故意的 对吧?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wow! That was on purpose, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 听着 伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. Look, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很优秀 但在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're good, yeah, but up here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,优秀和卓越是有区别的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}there's a difference between good and great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一比一 该你了 朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}1-1. Your turn, <i>amigo</i>.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我靠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fuck's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 看着 左门柱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right, watch this then. Left post.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 厉害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wow. That was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶!\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很幸运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-明天继续 杰米塔特? -再说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Again tomorrow, Jamie Tartt? -We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,足球就是生命!\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Football is life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼罗哈斯 罗哈斯!丹尼罗哈斯!\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dani Rojas, Rojas! Dani Rojas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 我跟你讲 伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, boy. I tell you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我们特别幸运 就像是从一棵幸运树上掉下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I feel like we fell out of a lucky tree, hit every branch on the way down,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掉进了一个装满现金 和先酸后甜的孩子们的水池\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}ended up in a pool full of cash and Sour Patch Kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:12:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰米是王牌 对吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, Jamie is an ace, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他的态度 让他变成了不受人待见的梅花7\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, whose attitude turned him into a seven of clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们找了另一个孩子 帮他重新变成王牌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So then we bring in another fella to help turn him back into an ace
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后那个孩子自己也会变成王牌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and then that fella ends up being an ace himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在我们有了两张王牌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And so now we got two aces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王牌 王牌 该死的 我又开始了 我没救了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Aces. Aces. Oh, heck. I did it again. I'm stuck.
