Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.98,0:28:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你意下如何 老板?离火近点暖和\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you say, boss? A lot warmer over there by the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.53,0:28:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不过去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll respectfully pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.45,0:28:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希金斯 你要来吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Higgins, coming with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.41,0:28:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.12,0:28:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 这是什么情况?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right now, what's this going on?
