Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.02,0:29:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.65,0:29:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你开除了杰米?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You got rid of Jamie?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.61,0:29:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曼城把他召回去的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Man City recalled him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.53,0:29:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说过了 泰德 他们很担心他没球可踢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I told you, Ted. They were concerned he wasn't playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.57,0:29:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我终于打开了他的心门!\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I finally got through to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.24,0:29:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, you saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.33,0:29:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了他和丹尼 我们手里就有两张王牌 瑞贝卡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}With him and Dani, we had two aces, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.95,0:29:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我以为那是你想要的 -你想错了!\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-I thought that was what you wanted. -Yeah, well, you thought wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.58,0:29:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我为我的语气道歉 我太粗鲁了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry. I'm sorry for my tone there, okay. That was rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.96,0:30:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我也想冷静 但我眼前一片红色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, I'm trying to be cool about this, but I am just seeing red everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.71,0:30:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你应该出去 免得口无遮拦说出什么让自己后悔的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, perhaps you should leave before you say something you'll regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.34,0:30:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你知道吗?这个给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, actually, you know what? Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.18,0:30:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的饼干\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your biscuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.27,0:30:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望和往常一样好吃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hope they're not as good as they usually are.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.23,0:30:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是该死的 他们是我带过的最好的球员 我原本已经搞定了!\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But dang it, they're the best batch yet. I finally cracked the recipe!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.95,0:30:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教练?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.28,0:30:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,足球就是生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Football is life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.51,0:30:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(塔特)
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.89,0:31:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,字幕翻译:肖雪

